    • updateStartGame

      void updateStartGame​(DevelopmentCard[][] cardsMarket, Marble[][] marbleMarket, Marble lonelyMarble, SoloToken soloToken, ThinPlayer actualPlayer, java.util.List<ThinPlayer> opponents)
      this method create the initial state of the thin model. in particular, once that every player did the initialization, this method set all the attributes to represent a complete game
      Parameters:
      cardsMarket - this is the cards market to set
      marbleMarket - this is the marble market to set
      lonelyMarble - this is the lonely marble to set
      soloToken - this is the solo token to set
      actualPlayer - this is the actual player to set
      opponents - these are the opponents to set
